title: Very useful
text: Very useful. It really helped to control my calorie intake. The ai does an amazing job of analysing my foods. It really simplifies the whole process! I'll keep using it

title: Would Recommend 10/10
text:
This is so useful! I’ve started using Calories.ai for 1 month and it’s already showing very promising results. 

I started at 186lbs and now I’m only 182lbs now. Let’s see how far this app can take me.

The interaction is very intuitive and I can easily get my daily meal photos down. Pretty neat.

Recommended. 
10/10
